<Base title="Usability Consulting" description="Usability consulting for continuous improvements to your online shop – Hob by Horse.">
<div class="lp"><section class="hero"><div class="hi">
<p class="kicker">Strategy</p>
<h1>Usability Consulting for Continuous Improvements to Your Online Shop</h1>
<p>We offer usability consulting as an advisory service for existing online shops or new developments. It concerns various assessments of current user-friendliness and improvement potential for individual adjustments or complete overhauls. Even a currently little-noticed online shop can achieve better market positioning and more customer approval in e-commerce.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>Usability Consulting by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>Usability describes, broadly translated, the user-friendliness of your online shop. More precisely, it is not merely the way of use itself, but also the offering of numerous operating options from which your target group can select the relevant ones. A pleasant shopping experience for customers is one they want to repeat. For this, we optimise usability already during the development of a website with the features of Shopware 6 and our additional software.</p>
<h2>Usability Consulting for Potential Utilisation in Several Phases</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Analytical consulting:</strong> This includes, for example, target audience analysis, process analysis and advice on existing projects before a project rescue or project takeover.</li>
<li><strong>Conceptual consulting/prototype development:</strong> This consulting area belongs to the detailed service of concept/conceptualisation in e-commerce and web.</li>
<li><strong>Design consulting:</strong> As web developers, we see exactly where your current design has weaknesses. At the same time, we offer to work out design-relevant strengths better and technically adapt them to the user experience.</li>
<li><strong>Review consulting:</strong> In the review, we define goals, concretise results and priorities, set a review date and align ourselves and your project team to the duration of the review.</li>
<li><strong>Relaunch consulting/requirement engineering:</strong> An important topic here is requirements management. A relaunch aims for a complete redesign of your online shop, either with the same content or through a complete range restructuring.</li>
<li><strong>Usability training:</strong> As an impulse workshop, it can give valuable suggestions for better shopping experiences and contemporary easy usability to your responsible team members.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Industry Sensitisation with Our Usability Consulting</h2>
<p>Within an industry, it is not promising to address all B2B trading partners equally and invite them to purchase in your online shop with the same functionality. Our usability consulting sensitises you to the expectations of specialist customers from manufacturing, processing and research sectors. B2C also plays an important role in simplicity and easy understanding.</p>
<h2>Usability Consulting by Hob by Horse for Better Target Group Understanding in E-Commerce</h2>
<p>You clearly know whether you want to sell your fashion items, lifestyle products or tourist services to end consumers or specialist audiences. However, you need to know exactly their trend interest, expectations and user behaviour according to changing market conditions. Usability consulting improves your strategic alignment for target groups in the automotive industry, shipbuilding, furniture manufacturing, food industry or education and healthcare sectors.</p>
<p><em>Would you like to book usability consulting as an impulse workshop? Present your online shop to Hob by Horse and discuss your current consulting needs by telephone or <a href="mailto:info@hob-by-horse.de">email</a>!</em></p>
</div></div>
</Base>
